# Instructions
Submit the following command in terminal
Replace the PM_API_KEY variable with your API key

```
curl --location 'https://api.promethium.qcware.com/v0/workflows' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--header 'Accept: application/json' \
--header 'X-API-Key: PM_API_KEY' \
--data '{
    "name": "nirmatrelvir_api_spc",
    "version": "v1",
    "kind": "SinglePointCalculation",
    "parameters": {
        "molecule": {
            "base64data": "",
            "filetype": "xyz"},
        "system": {
            "params": {
                "basisname": "def2-tzvp",
                "jkfit_basisname": "def2-universal-jkfit",
                "methodname": "wb97m-v",
                "xc_grid_scheme": "SG2"
            }
        },
        "hf": {
            "params": {"charge": 0, "multiplicity": 1, "g_convergence": 0.000001},
            "outputs": {
                "gradient": false,
                "polarizability": false,
                "dipole_derivative": false
            }
        }
    },
    "resources": {"gpu_type": "a100"}
}'
```
